            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h3>Civic Garden</h3>
<p>The Lansdowne Civic Garden is a demonstration garden with 26 beds featuring different themes. Food harvested from the garden is donated to the Centretown Emergency Food Centre. The Ethno-Botanical beds feature plant species of ceremonial, medicinal or practical use in Algonquin culture.</p>
